💜 Hey everyone! I’m on the new year buzz of wanting to look my best for 2024!! I wanted to do a little chat about this awesome new wellness and skincare company I discovered recently. It’s called @myinvity and it specialises in amazing innovative products that contain NAD, which is a coenzyme that is responsible for metabolism, cognitive health and much more! I’m trying their beautiful skincare products and supplements. I’ll put up on my stories the textures of the products so you can see! I’m really into this so thought doing a video to share with you would be great to spread the word about how great and innovative this range is!! If you want to be properly inspired and learn about the brand check out their IG page @myinvity #skincareroutine #newproductalert #skincarewithsjwai #2024newyearsresolutions
